		Gowin_PicoRV32 MCU Hardware Reference Design
--------------------------------------------------------------
Frequency
	50MHz
--------------------------------------------------------------
DVK
	DK_START_GW2A18_V2.0
--------------------------------------------------------------
Chip
	GW2A-18
	GW2A-LV18PG256C8/I7
--------------------------------------------------------------
CORE
	Trap Stack Overflow
	Debug
--------------------------------------------------------------
DTCM
	Size : 32KB
	Enable Hardware Stack Protection : 0x7FFF
--------------------------------------------------------------
ITCM
	Size : 32KB
	MCU boot from external Flash and run in ITCM
--------------------------------------------------------------
Reference Design
	gowin_picorv32
		Peripherals
			Simple UART
			WB UART
			WB I2C Master
			WB SPI Master
			WB SPI Slave
			WB GPIO
			ADV SPI-Flash
			OPEN WB INTERFACE
			OPEN AHB INTERFACE
			User Interrupt Handler
	Synthesis Tool
		GowinSynthesis
--------------------------------------------------------------
IDE
	Gowin_V1.9.6 Beta and higher
